SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_id||'"', '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v5.days_code||'"', '"'||v6.day_name||'"', v6.year,
 v6.month_number, v6.day_number, v0.arrival_time FROM flight v0,
 airport_service v1, city v2, airport_service v3, city v4,
 days v5, date_day v6

sql: ( SELECT DISTINCT FLIGHT.FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' BALTIMORE ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' SAN FRANCISCO ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME IN ( SELECT DATE_DAY.DAY_NAME FROM DATE_DAY WHERE DATE_DAY.YEAR = 1993 AND DATE_DAY.MONTH_NUMBER = 3 AND DATE_DAY.DAY_NUMBER = 5 ) ) AND FLIGHT.ARRIVAL_TIME < 2000 ) ) ) ) ;
